CLARION CONSULTS ON AFFORDABLE HOUSING SCHEME IN RICHMOND
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Clarion Housing Group plans to deliver much-needed affordable
    housing in the borough of Richmond.

    Under the proposals, which are being consulted on during September
    2018, the Group will develop 180 new affordable homes on Egerton
    Road - the former Richmond College site. Of these homes, 154 will
    be for shared ownership and 26 will be for affordable rent.

